---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const lastUpdated = "July 29, 2025";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Pyonet Apps">
  <main class="privacy-container">
    <section class="privacy-content">
      <h1>Privacy Policy – Pyonet Apps</h1>
      <p>
        <strong>Pyonet.com</strong> (“we,” “our,” or “us”) is committed to protecting
        your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard
        your data when you use our mobile applications developed by Pyonet.com (the
        “App” or “Apps”).
      </p>

      <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
      <p>
        Pyonet.com is an online-based software agency that builds modern,
        helpful apps like Azaan App and Split-Mate. Our goal is to improve daily
        life through clean, user-focused technology.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email, phone number, profile
          info (if applicable)
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Device & Usage:</strong> Device type, app interactions, crash reports
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Optional Info:</strong> User content like expense notes, preferences
          (only if you submit it)
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To deliver and improve app functionality</li>
        <li>Send notifications or updates (when enabled)</li>
        <li>Fix bugs and analyze usage</li>
        <li>Comply with laws and protect against misuse</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your personal data. We may share data:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>With trusted partners (hosting, analytics)</li>
        <li>With legal authorities if required</li>
        <li>With other users only if you choose to share content</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Children’s Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Our apps are not intended for children under 13. If we learn that data
        has been collected from a child without parental consent, we will delete
        it.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Data Security and Retention</h2>
      <p>
        We use secure servers and encryption to protect your data. Information
        is kept only as long as necessary to deliver our services.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Access or update your data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your account or information</li>
        <li>Control notifications and sharing settings</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        To contact us, email: <a href="mailto:privacy@pyonet.com"
          >privacy@pyonet.com</a
        >
      </p>

      <h2>8. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        We may use services like Google Analytics, Firebase, or AdMob which
        collect usage data anonymously. External links or content may follow
        different privacy practices.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy periodically. The latest version will always
        be available here.
      </p>

      <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Pyonet.com</strong><br />
        Email: <a href="mailto:info@pyonet.com">info@pyonet.com</a><br />
        Website: <a href="https://pyonet.com" target="_blank"
          >https://pyonet.com</a
        >
      </p>

      <p class="last-updated"><em>Last Updated: {lastUpdated}</em></p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <style>
    .privacy-container {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;

      color: var(--foreground, #f1f5f9);
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .privacy-content {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: auto;
      background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.7);
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .privacy-content h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #60a5fa, #a78bfa);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .privacy-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      color: #facc15;
    }

    .privacy-content p,
    .privacy-content ul {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-top: 0.6rem;
    }

    .privacy-content ul {
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
    }

    .privacy-content a {
      color: #38bdf8;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .last-updated {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #94a3b8;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .privacy-content {
        padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
      }

      .privacy-content h1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      .privacy-content h2 {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      .privacy-content p,
      .privacy-content ul {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
